query:
WITH inserted AS (
                    INSERT INTO tag (label, created_by, color)
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                    RETURNING tag.id, tag.label, tag.created_by, tag.color, tag.last_used_at
                )
                SELECT
                    i.id as "id!",
                    i.label as "label!",
                    i.created_by as "created_by!",
                    i.color as "color!",
                    i.last_used_at as "last_used_at!"
                FROM inserted i
